---
title: Pork Shawarma Bowl with Cucumber-Lemon Couscous, Red Cabbage Slaw and Tahini Sauce
description: We sprinkled juicy pork chops with a shawarma spice blend and added some traditional Middle Eastern fixin's —  tahini and pickled cabbage! — to create this delicious dinner bowl.
